Trichet Calls Europe ‘Epicenter’ of Credit Crisis, Urges Governance Change

-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 
2011-07-10T07:47:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-10/trichet-calls-europe-epicenter-of-credit-crisis-urges-governance-change.html
European Central Bank President
 Jean-Claude Trichet  said  Europe  is at the “epicenter” of a
debt crisis that concerns the entire developed world and urged
the euro area to do the “maximum” in terms of governance
reforms. He spoke at a conference in Aix-en-Provence,  France .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mark Deen in Aix-en-Provence, France at 
 markdeen@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
